{"tid":1732650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾和理非同我入曬黎","createTime":"2019-11-18T02:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T03:28:33.000Z","uid":236124,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"46c64091f8859b2cae379bba014bbc433c3a34f9","tid":1732650,"uid":236124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:39:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔知出到去可以做到咩<br />\n但我知唔出去一定咩都做唔到!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n你地諗緊d咩?<br />\n罷左工但係仲留係屋企? 不如你都係返工<br />\n出面要人啊!!!<br />\n我知道尖沙咀好危險 可能會比大圍捕<br />\n但係你諗下  理大手足支持左咁耐 挨唔住架啦<br />\n佢地等緊我地呢班和理非 <br />\n<br />\n大不了其實都係被捕 <br />\n其實無野好驚<br />\n一係繼續做港豬 <br />\n一係就出黎啦!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1230 出佐敦尖沙咀 和你Lunch好無?</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n出左黎先有機會聚到人<br />\n<br />\n一個單拖垃圾和理絲上"},{"pid":"78b9183239c5b8f966eb3c62122df287127282f4","tid":1732650,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NdgS8Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NdgS8Y.jpg&h=fb14efa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n老豆搵仔呼籲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你仲返工？去理大啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不落單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不譴責<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不退縮"},{"pid":"a964d4efb28eb3546076ebda0803a561d46e68e1","tid":1732650,"uid":207543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:44:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. 救人先 檢討後<br />\n2. 唔完美 理性講<br />\n3. 多體諒 少怪責<br />\n4. 遇分化 冷處理</span></span><br />\n辛苦曬po主同手足<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"70045ad5db64a741c0d08f13b4c9671d45ff645e","tid":1732650,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime